<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV102">
<l>viḷavilāta kātalāl viḷaṅkupāta pōtilvait</l>
<l>tuḷḷuvēṉa tūṉanōyo ḻikkumāte ḻikkunīrp</l>
<l>paḷḷimāya paṉṟiyāya veṉṟivīra kuṉṟiṉāṟ</l>
<l>ṟuḷḷunīrva rampuceyta tōṉṟaloṉṟu colliṭē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tell me about a path that destroys the disease that is the body,</l>
<l>for me who think about [Your] lustrous lotus feet out of unbreaking love,</l>
<l>O wonderful [Lord] who lis on the roaring ocean! O victorious Warrior</l>
<l>Who became a boar! O King who made a path with hills across the leaping sea!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
